---
<section class="mission" id="mission-command">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mission-inner">
      <div class="mission-content">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">Go Deeper</div>
        <h2>Mission Command</h2>
        <p class="mission-price">$19 <span>/month</span></p>
        <p class="mission-sub">
          The Weekly Brief gets you the intelligence. Mission Command gets you the battle plans.
        </p>
        <ul class="mission-list">
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Deep-dive implementation guides</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Full playbooks across all 6 Levers</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Behind-the-scenes build logs</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Priority access to new frameworks</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> 7-day free trial — no commitment</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.beehiiv.com/subscribe/richer-living" class="btn btn-primary mission-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Start 7-Day Free Trial
        </a>
        <p class="mission-note">Cancel any time. No questions asked.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mission-quote">
        <blockquote>
          "A job is a single point of failure. An engine runs whether you're at the desk 
          or on a beach in Barcelona. Mission Command is where you learn to build the engine."
        </blockquote>
        <cite>— Richer Living, The Framework</cite>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    background: var(--navy-light);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
  }

  .mission-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .mission-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .mission-price {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .mission-price span {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gray);
  }

  .mission-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .mission-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .mission-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-light);
  }

  .check {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .mission-cta {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
  }

  .mission-note {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .mission-quote {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 2.5rem;
  }

  .mission-quote blockquote {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--off-white);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mission-quote cite {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .mission-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .mission-quote {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
